OL,7,FIn an interview ahead of the release
OL,8,Fof her new drama Code of Silence, the
OL,9,Factor Rose Ayling Ellis tells ITV News
OL,10,FArts Editor Nina Nannar that
OL,11,Fbroadcasters need to be a little bit
OL,12,Fbraver when it comes to making dramas
OL,13,Fabout, and starring, deaf people.
OL,15,FAs someone who wears a hearing aid,
OL,16,FITV's new drama is of particular
OL,17,Finterest to me.
OL,19,FI got tinnitus two decades ago, which
OL,20,FI still have, like a fax machine
OL,21,Fcontinually sounding in my head.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
