OL,7,FIt was accompanied by hearing loss,
OL,8,Fhence the hearing aid and my
OL,9,Foccasional attempts to lip read when
OL,10,FI'm in a crowded noisy pub.
OL,12,FAnd I have to say Code of Silence
OL,13,Fstarring Rose Ayling-Ellis, gets this
OL,14,Fexperience right.
OL,16,FLip reading is really hard, and it
OL,17,Fwould be tempting for this drama to
OL,18,Fmake it look easy, to focus in on the
OL,19,Fmouth of the person being read,
OL,20,Fsomething which Ayling-Ellis made sure
OL,21,Fthe cameras did not do.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
