OL,7,FAs Executive Producer on the drama,
OL,8,Fshe was determined to get the
OL,9,Fportrayal of lip reading by deaf
OL,10,Fpeople like her as accurate as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FIt helps that the screenwriter on the
OL,14,Fdrama is partially deaf herself.
OL,16,FWhat Catherine Moulton wanted to bring
OL,17,Fto the story of a deaf canteen worker,
OL,18,Fwho is enlisted to help the police
OL,19,Ffoil a crime, was authenticity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
