OL,7,FBetween her and Ayling-Ellis ,who
OL,8,Fplays the lead Alison, and other deaf
OL,9,Fmembers of the cast, it has worked.
OL,11,FPeople can't lip read if the person
OL,12,Fthey are looking at has their mouth
OL,13,Fcovered, and it is really difficult if
OL,14,Fyou can't see the way the person is
OL,15,Fbehaving, their body language.
OL,17,FLip reading is all those things, and
OL,18,Feven then you might not get more than
OL,19,F40% of what someone is saying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
