OL,7,FIt keeps her in work, but she's also
OL,8,Fintent on making a difference, which
OL,9,Fshe hopes Code of Silence will do.
OL,11,F"Why didn't I have programmes like
OL,12,Fthis when I was growing up?" she asks.
OL,14,FDeaf people remain underrepresented on
OL,15,Fscreen and behind the scenes in TV
OL,16,Fwith one report showing they make up
OL,17,Fless than 1% of the UK broadcast
OL,18,Findustry.
